       The small transport landed on a platform by the Iron Fist. Ominous and 
Akron exited the vessle and approached Devilduer.
       "I am Ominous Prime. Here to talk to your Commander." He said, looking 
around the impressive ship. It was a lot bigger, and a lot more powerful.
       Akron breathed deeply, this planet was truly beautiful....to bad they 
were going to have to ruin it all though.

--part1_7d.e7ffda9.27715dda_boundary
